header.gameNote: AIR FORCE RESERVE BASKETBALL HALL OF FAME CLASSIC

videos.description: Luguentz Dort picks Cody Martin's pocket and takes it all the way to the rim, finishing with a sweet reverse layup to continue the Sun Devils' hot start.
videos.headline: ASU's Dort steals and scores with reverse layup

videos.description: Zylan Cheatham cuts backdoor and finishes through the contact for a 3-point play, extending Arizona State's 1st-half lead over Nevada.
videos.headline: Cheatham takes contact for tough and-1

videos.description: Jordan Caroline chucks an inbounds pass all the way down the court, and Jazz Johnson drains a jumper to beat the first-half buzzer.
videos.headline: Caroline launches football pass to Johnson to beat buzzer

videos.description: Cody Martin comes off the screen and throws it to the rim for Trey Porter, who finishes with a huge alley-oop flush.
videos.headline: Martin lobs, Porter slams

videos.description: Trey Porter snatches the ball right out of Romello White's hands on the layup attempt, and Caleb Martin converts for a 3-point play on the other end.
videos.headline: Porter's nasty denial leads to Martin's and-1

videos.description: Zylan Cheatham lobs it to the rim, and Luguentz Dort takes care of the rest, hammering home a strong two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Cheatham lobs to Dort for alley-oop jam

videos.description: Tre'Shawn Thurman swings it to Caleb Martin, who knocks it through from downtown to give the Wolf Pack their first lead since 1-0.
videos.headline: Martin puts Nevada in front with 3-ball

videos.description: Caleb Martin drives baseline and draws the defense before making a beautiful pass to Tre'Shawn Thurman, who battles through contact for the 3-point play.
videos.headline: Martin drives and dishes to Thurman for and-1
